Text: I've put in Ccleaner's Business Edition as well as the normal freeware which is available out there and so far I've yet to see a difference between them. Can someone enlighten me?
@bert16 the only dif is that you get support with the business ed
That's true, but to get support at all you have to buy it. I doubt they'll help you out if they found out your copy came from here :-)
